---
// src/pages/returns.astro
import InfoPageLayout from '../layouts/InfoPageLayout.astro';
---

<InfoPageLayout 
  title="Returns Policy" 
  description="Fresh Wax returns and refunds policy. 14-day returns on physical products, full refund policy for damaged items."
>
  <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
    We want you to be completely happy with your purchase. If something isn't right, here's how we can help.
  </p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>
    Under the Consumer Contracts Regulations 2013, you have the right to cancel your order within 14 days of receiving your goods, for any reason. This is in addition to your statutory rights under the Consumer Rights Act 2015.
  </p>

  <h2>Physical Products (Vinyl, Merch)</h2>
  
  <h3>14-Day Returns</h3>
  <p>You can return physical products within 14 days of delivery if:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The item is unused and in original condition</li>
    <li>Vinyl is still sealed (unopened)</li>
    <li>Clothing has tags attached and is unworn</li>
    <li>Original packaging is intact</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Damaged or Faulty Items</h3>
  <p>
    If your order arrives damaged or faulty, we'll replace it or issue a full refund including return shipping costs. Please:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Contact us within 48 hours of delivery</li>
    <li>Provide photos of the damage</li>
    <li>Keep all packaging until the issue is resolved</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Wrong Item Received</h3>
  <p>
    If we sent you the wrong item, contact us immediately and we'll arrange collection and send the correct item at no extra cost.
  </p>

  <h3>Non-Returnable Items</h3>
  <p>The following items cannot be returned unless faulty:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Opened/unsealed vinyl records</li>
    <li>Worn clothing or items without tags</li>
    <li>Personalised or custom-made items</li>
    <li>Sale items marked as "Final Sale"</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Digital Downloads</h2>
  <div class="bg-gray-100 border-l-4 border-black p-4 mb-6">
    <p class="font-semibold">Important: Digital downloads are non-refundable</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">
      Once you've downloaded a digital product, we cannot offer a refund. By purchasing digital content, you acknowledge that you waive your right to cancel once the download begins.
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <p>Exceptions may be made if:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The files are corrupted and cannot be re-downloaded</li>
    <li>The product was significantly misrepresented</li>
    <li>Technical issues on our end prevented access</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How to Return</h2>
  
  <h3>Step 1: Contact Us</h3>
  <p>
    Email <a href="mailto:returns@freshwax.co.uk">returns@freshwax.co.uk</a> with:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your order number</li>
    <li>Items you wish to return</li>
    <li>Reason for return</li>
    <li>Photos (if damaged/faulty)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Step 2: Receive Authorisation</h3>
  <p>
    We'll review your request and send you a Return Authorisation Number (RAN) and return instructions within 2 working days.
  </p>

  <h3>Step 3: Ship the Item</h3>
  <p>
    Pack the item securely and ship to the address provided. Include the RAN on the outside of the package.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Change of mind returns:</strong> You pay return shipping</li>
    <li><strong>Damaged/faulty/wrong item:</strong> We'll provide a prepaid label or refund shipping costs</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Step 4: Receive Refund</h3>
  <p>
    Once we receive and inspect your return, we'll process your refund within 5-7 working days. Refunds are issued to the original payment method.
  </p>

  <h2>Refund Timeline</h2>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
    <table class="w-full border-collapse">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-black text-white">
          <th class="p-3 text-left">Payment Method</th>
          <th class="p-3 text-left">Refund Time</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="p-3">Credit/Debit Card</td>
          <td class="p-3">5-10 working days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
          <td class="p-3">PayPal</td>
          <td class="p-3">3-5 working days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
          <td class="p-3">Store Credit</td>
          <td class="p-3">Immediate</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2>Exchanges</h2>
  <p>
    We don't offer direct exchanges. If you need a different size or variant, please return the original item for a refund and place a new order. This ensures you get the item you want without waiting.
  </p>

  <h2>Pre-Orders</h2>
  <p>
    Pre-orders can be cancelled for a full refund at any time before the item ships. Once shipped, standard return policies apply.
  </p>

  <h2>International Returns</h2>
  <p>
    International customers are responsible for return shipping costs unless the item was damaged, faulty, or incorrectly sent. Please note:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Mark returns as "Returned Goods" on customs forms</li>
    <li>We are not responsible for customs charges on returns</li>
    <li>Use a tracked shipping service for your protection</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Questions?</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about returns, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a> or email <a href="mailto:returns@freshwax.co.uk">returns@freshwax.co.uk</a>.
  </p>
</InfoPageLayout>